name: Qualys: assets that have not been scanned within the past 2 weeks
Qualys: vulnerabilities with publicly available exploits
Qualys: vulnerabilities that can lead to high data loss
Qualys: vulnerabilities leading to denial of service
Qualys: vulnerabilities that allow for unauthenticated exploitation
Qualys: vulnerabilities that allow remote code execution
Qualys: critical severity vulnerabilities that are on CISA's Known Exploited list
description: Critical vulnerabilities are to be remediated within 15 days per CISA guidance.
query: source:qualys AND severity:critical AND (vulnerability.threatIntel:"%Cisa_Known_Exploited_Vulns%" OR kev:cisa)

name: Qualys: high severity vulnerabilities that are on CISA's Known Exploited list
description: High severity vulnerabilities are to be remediated within 30 days per CISA guidance.
query: source:qualys AND severity:high AND (vulnerability.threatIntel:"%Cisa_Known_Exploited_Vulns%" OR kev:cisa)

name: Qualys: assets with Qualys endpoint agent installed
Qualys: reported by Qualys but do not have the endpoint agent installed
Qualys: reported by qualys and found via vuln scan
Qualys: endpoints that could host a Qualys endpoint agent but do not have one installed
query: NOT @qualys.dev.host.trackingMethod:="AGENT" AND (type:server OR type:laptop OR type:desktop)
